description: Lists all approval rule templates that are associated with a specified repository.

parameters.name: repositoryName
parameters.description: The name of the repository for which you want to list all associated approval rule templates.

nested_items.name: approvalRuleTemplateNames
nested_items.description: The names of all approval rule templates associated with the repository.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: An enumeration token that allows the operation to batch the next results of the operation.
